<div>
WEEK 2&nbsp;<a href=\"https://plus.google.com/events/cgqvrqkvv5enc6naj14f0smgle8?authkey=CIHx6pqVwYP-4QE&amp;e=PlusPageAnalytics\">「最適化のヒント〜基本編〜」</a></div>
